item.dc:creator: Tmaned
item.description:
Cup o Joe:

These games look sort of like a computer version of legos.

That’s pretty much what it is. You can build some cool stuff, but the smacktard kids who don’t know how to stack virtual blocks will get jealous and try to destroy it.
